# .ossify_seeds — manual override list for tool/ossify.hexa
#
# Plain text, one path per line. Lines starting with '#' are comments.
# Blank lines are ignored.
#
# This file lets you pin non-.hexa files (binaries, generated blobs, seed
# artifacts) for OS-level immutability, bypassing the @ossify header scan.
# The scan in tool/ossify.hexa also picks up any .hexa / .json file whose
# first non-comment line is exactly "@ossify" — so you only need to add
# paths here for files that can't embed the attr header.
#
# Examples (commented out — do NOT actually apply to frozen seeds):
# build/hexa_stage0
# self/native/hexa_v2

# Smoke-test scratch target — safe to keep (outside repo tree):
/tmp/hx_ossify_test.hexa
